Class TableColumnHeaderBuilder

java.lang.Object
io.github.sosuisen.jfxbuilder.controls.TableColumnHeaderBuilder
public class TableColumnHeaderBuilder extends Object
The TableColumnHeaderBuilder class constructs instances of the TableColumnHeader class and offers a fluent interface for creating and configuring it.

This class includes a static create method that accepts the same arguments as the original TableColumnHeader constructor and returns an instance of the TableColumnHeaderBuilder.

You can use method chaining to call the builder methods for configuring the TableColumnHeader. Finally, invoke the build method to generate an instance of the TableColumnHeader class.

Note that intermediate builder methods are not evaluated until the build method is called, meaning they are evaluated lazily.

Author:
Hidekazu Kubota <hidekazu.kubota@gmail.com>
